    "synopsis": "Series-start Dark Hunters novel. The chapter — a White-Scars successor whose silent-hunting doctrine descends from the Sahrmatae of homeworld Phobian — repulses a Chaos raid that turns out to be a feint. The real campaign is on Ras Hanem, where the Punishers, a warband the chapter believed destroyed years before, have returned for vengeance and are marauding its hive cities. Captain Jonah Kerne of Mortai Company leads the response: a slow-burning pursuit through fortified districts, joint-arms with PDF and Imperial Guard, and a decapitation strike at the warband's command. A grim chapter-portrait that closes on the motto's literal meaning — we are the shadow.",
